review_title: All works well, I'll take it...
reviews: I didn't need a camcorder, I seen this one on sale and thought, well looks like a good deal. So i bought this for some reason. Everything works just fine, In and outdoors it takes a nice clear picture, the videos cam works great, very easy to operate. All of a sudden i need this, just cause !! It's so cute small and portable, has a flip screen, comes with everything, well made and nice design, easy to charge up, led light Indicator for charging and when mic is on, are all working good. Easy to transfer pics & video's to computer. The videos also look great on the big screen TV. Good little camcorder this is. I'll take it...

review_title: Not just For Youths, Adults Also...
reviews: I'm over 50 years old, male 5' 5" tall 130 lbs. I've been Looking everywhere for a pair knee/shin pads for when I'm on my Yamaha bolt 950cc motorcycle to protect me from flying rocks, bugs and cold winds when on the highway.. I have a pair of jeans and my insulated Rain pants on. To start! These pads go on fast and easy. They fit so nice , Very Light, They stay up, You forget you have them on. There perfect for me and what in need them for, and very well built, good looking Pads with a cool storage bag. Wow Very nice. I would like to thank everyone who left there feedback, Between the Adult size and the youth size. After reading all there feedback. I went with the youth size, and a perfect fit they are. If I lose these I will Order Again. Also; Amazon Rules...
Easy to put together, well built, very nice.
